'Feasibility' may refer to:

*Logical possibility, that which is achievable. *Feasible region, a region that
satisfies mathematical constraints *Feasibility study, a preliminary study to
determine a project's viability. *[[Feasibility Study (The Outer
Limits)|Feasibility Study]], an episode of The Outer Limits TV show.
